reviewText:
Early Access Review

Brilliant shmup, its been some time since I played a good game of this genre:
Good music, gets you pumped for some side scrolling shooting action.
Enemies are (so far) diverse.
Well balanced game in my opinion, when I die, it feels like my fault, not the games fault.
Nice mix of 3d and 2d backgrounds, from the menu to the actual gameplay.All in all, especially for a Early Access game, its a good side scrolling shooter, hell, some Early Access games that have been on Steam longer have less content then this.
I hope the developers keep going in this direction, and listen to community feedback.
